data.description: Welcome to this 3 bedroom and 1.5 bath cape cod. Nice on interior, some handyman work needed on exterior. Gleaming hardwood floors throughout the living area. The home has a lot of older woodwork, which adds character. The kitchen has ample counter and cabinet space. There is a full basement for extra storage. Enclosed front porch welcomes you in. House was mostly updated back in 2014 with. Kitchen & baths w/granite counter & ceramic floors. A/C, newer roof on house & garage installed in 2014. New attic insulation in 2020, new fence 2020, water heater 2021, windows & garage just painted in 2023. Chimney flashing new in 2023. Large fenced yard, extra long driveway & lots of bsmt storage. 1 car garage w/driveway. Close to local parks and restaurants.
